creator: Tap Electric
descriptionHtml:
Tap Electric takes care of charging your car.

With Tap Electric, charging has never been simpler. Just open the app, tap on your favourite charger and plug in your car.

Do you want to know a bit more before you start charging? How about prices? We show the complete price for every charger in our app. No hidden fees, ever. Do you want to find updates during the charging? We'll show you energy charged, current speed of charging and the cost of charging so far.

Do you want to know if a charger will be available tonight? We'll show you predictions for the entire day.

Is your preferred charger occupied by someone else? Don't worry! With Tap Charging Groups you easily reach out to other users. Together you'll make sure everyone can charge.

Are you not ready for a commitment? That's fine - all of our charging features are accessible without having to create an account. You'll be charging in no time.

So, what's the catch? How are we able to do this? Well, Tap is not for everyone. Because of our strict quality criteria for chargers before letting them on our app, you will not find every public charger in our app. Yet.

Haven't found a charger in your neighbourhood? Be sure to come back later - our networks grows with the minute.

title: Tap Electric - Charge your car

creator: Tap Electric
descriptionHtml:
Easy payments for car charging.

Tap Electric is quite simply the best charging app for drivers, packed full of features while staying true to our maxim: get charging with just one Tap. Get started with no account to see why drivers love us: super intuitive features to find and use chargers, incredibly easy payments, and no hidden fees, ever.

Do you need to collect payments on your own charger? Whether you are an airbnb host with a single charger, or an operator with 1000 parking lots to manage, Tap Electric can turn your chargers into a business overnight. Get a charger live within 1 minute and start collecting payments immediately, for free -- that's right, not a trial period, not “freemium”, just free.

FOR DRIVERS
Find a charger
* AI-supported insights in (predicted) charger availability
* Get notified when a charger becomes available
* Access to charger networks across Europe and the UK
* We filter unreliable chargers out of the app to make sure you can always find one that works.

Haven't found a charger in your neighbourhood? Be sure to come back later - our network grows by the minute.

Easy payments
* Charge as a guest or with an account
* Charge straight from the app or RFID
* Pay per session with Google Pay or Mastercard / VISA or subscribe to pay per month
* Subscription plans available with and without RFID Tapkey
* Insight in invoices
* Fully transparent pricing for every charger, no hidden fees.

Manage your costs
* Auto-stop to automatically stop the session at given energy, duration or cost. * Real-time cost calculations for charge sessions

In-app messaging
* P2P messaging based on license plate
* Group messaging based on charger / site

FOR OWNERS OF CHARGERS
Get started quickly
* Connect with chargers and manage them in the app
* See charge sessions on your chargers
* Offer ad-hoc, subscription and RFID payments to drivers

Manage chargers
* See connectivity and live status

Manage tariffs
* Set special ‘admin’ tariffs
* Set reimbursement tariffs

Manage payouts
* Manage payouts straight from the app

Manage accessibility
* Hide chargers from the public
* Invite admins

creator: Tap Electric
descriptionHtml:
Seriously. Good EV charging.

Start charging now – no account needed. Our app is packed with features for EV drivers to help you get the most out of your EV charging with just one tap.

Find trusted electric vehicle chargers
• We only show you EV charging points that actually work and filter out the rest to save you time
• See insights on charger availability so you can better plan your day
• Find charge points based on charging speed, price, location and energy mix to fit your car needs
• Get notified when a charging station becomes available near you
• Discover cheaper electric chargers nearby with our EV charge map
• Access our growing public charger network in NL, UK and Europe
• Find charge points powered by green energy
• Easily navigate to electric vehicle charging stations

Know how much you pay before you start a charge session
• Get real-time cost calculations for every EV charger
• No hidden fees, we believe in fully transparent pricing inclusive of tariffs
• Charge straight from the app or with a Tap charge key (RFID charge card)
• Safe and secure payments for each session with Google Pay, Visa, Mastercard, iDeal
• Get invoices for your charge sessions
• See your charging history, statistics and invoicing even in guest mode

Auto-stop your charge sessions
• Automatically stop your charging session at your set energy, duration or cost

Save on your charging costs with Tap Electric
• Save up to 10% on transaction fees on every charge session when you subscribe
• Get a Tap charge key (RFID charge card) with some subscriptions for quick payment

Our Tap key is the world’s first charging key to come with built-in security against theft, copying or emulating.

Share feedback that helps other EV drivers find the right charger
• Comment on charging points by locations and sites, we never want an EV charger to ruin anyone’s day
• Privately message others via their licence plate
• Send group messages based on chargers or sites

If you own an EV charger, you can also manage your chargers with Tap Electric for free.

Get your electric vehicle charger live in minutes and start collecting payments from your airbnb, home or 1000+ charger station using our free charge management software.

Did you know that many airbnb hosts already offer their chargers to their guests exclusively with Tap Electric payments?

• Connect your chargers and manage them all in one place
• Offer ad-hoc, subscription and RFID payments to electric vehicle drivers
• Manage tariffs, set special ‘admin’ and reimbursement tariffs
• See charge sessions of your chargers
• Check connectivity and live status
• Manage payments and payouts straight from the app
• Hide chargers from the public whenever you need to
• Set up controls by inviting admins
